{{Quote|You all right, pera?''"<br />"''Yes, my fi.|Han Solo and Pera|<ref name="Star Wars (1977) 7">[[Star Wars (1977) 7|''Star Wars'' (1977) 7]]</ref>}}
"'''Fi'''" was a [[High Galactic (language)|High Galactic]] expression used by clergymen following the [[Sacred Way/Legends|Sacred Way]] as a term of address directed at non-clergymen. It meant "male child" and was used specifically with male sentients. [[Grand Admiral/Legends|Grand Admiral]] [[Peccati Syn]] later named [[Silooth (Star Destroyer)|his Star Destroyer]] after the word.

